{"tid":685284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港人月入中位數$1.8萬　建造業最多人就業不足","createTime":"2018-05-31T09:49:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T14:28:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a34e04b95881564c70ed9650b541031a5361ff3b","tid":685284,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"統計處發表今年首季，即1至3月的《綜合住戶統計調查按季統計報告》，期間勞動人口為398.44萬人，較去年同期增加3.7萬多人，較上季多2萬多人。撇除外傭後，今年第1季勞動人口達366.77萬人。<br />\n<br />\n今年首季的失業人數則為11.2萬多人，較去年同期下跌。首季就業人士每月就業收入中位數為16,400港元。撇除外籍家庭傭工後為1.8萬港元，較去年同期分別上升1400港元及1500港元。另外，有12.4%的就業人士每月就業收入少於5000港元，有10.5%每月就業收入則為5萬港元或以上。<br />\n<br />\n首季的就業不足人數為38,900人，較去年同期下跌逾萬人，但從事建造業、地基及上蓋工程業，以及樓房裝飾、修葺及保養業就有較多的就業不足人士，分別佔總就業不足人數的44.4%、27.6%及16.8%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/bkn-20180531165146545-0531_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180531%2Fbkn-20180531165146545-0531_00822_001.html&d=nmvs43czZi76FBiUJ2hPmQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bd882b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180531/bkn-20180531165146545-0531_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"25be7a9139980b9f72f02f282fd38e63ec86049b","tid":685284,"uid":12021,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"85fc601ae4deadd1459e554c7a51d9bacc97b012","tid":685284,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"有10.5%係連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551ff5cf49849c8dd373e5616563fa0c0d88b7a8","tid":685284,"uid":19363,"like":4,"dislike":0,"sco